and from English domination. The altered short form <i>Bob</i> is very common, but <i>Hob</i> and <i>Dob</i>, which were common in the Middle Ages and gave rise to surnames, are extinct.  See also  Rupert ."],"variants":[]}],"lifeSummary":"Robert Copendale was born in 1118. He married Mrs Robert Copendale before 1144, in England. They were the parents of at least 1 daughter."},"et":{"<1118>–":"1118–Surnud","–Female":"Surnud","1144–Female":"1144–Surnud","1118–Male":"1118–Surnud","1118":"1118","<1118>":"1118","before 1144":"enne 1144","1144":"1144","about 1144":"umbes 1144","Beverley, Yorkshire, England":"Beverley, Yorkshire, England","England":"England"},"fi":{"<1118>–":"1118–Kuollut","–Female":"Kuollut","1144–Female":"1144–Kuollut","1118–Male":"1118–Kuollut","1118":"1118","<1118>":"1118","before 1144":"ennen vuotta 1144","1144":"1144","about 1144":"noin 1144","Beverley, Yorkshire, England":"Beverley, Yorkshire, England","England":"England"},"fr":{"<1118>–":"1118–Décédé","–Female":"Décédée","1144–Female":"1144–Décédée","1118–Male":"1118–Décédé","1118":"1118","<1118>":"1118","before 1144":"avant 1144","1144":"1144","about 1144":"environ 1144","Beverley, Yorkshire, England":"Beverley, Everwyck, Angleterre","England":"Angleterre","lifeSummary":"Robert Copendale est né en 1118. Il a épousé Mrs Robert Copendale avant 1144, à Angleterre. Ils ont eu au moins 1 fille."},"de":{"<1118>–":"1118–Verstorben","–Female":"Verstorben","1144–Female":"1144–Verstorben","1118–Male":"1118–Verstorben","1118":"1118","<1118>":"1118","before 1144":"vor 1144","1144":"1144","about 1144":"um 1144","Beverley, Yorkshire, England":"Beverley, Yorkshire, England","England":"England","lifeSummary":"Robert Copendale wurde 1118 geboren. Er hat vor 1144 in England Mrs Robert Copendale geheiratet. Sie hatten mindestens 1 Tochter."},"ht":{"<1118>–":"1118–Desede","–Female":"Desede","1144–Female":"1144–Desede","1118–Male":"1118–Desede","1118":"1118","<1118>":"1118","before 1144":"before 1144","1144":"1144","